---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Amanda Vilela | Frontend Specialist"
description: "Frontend specialist with 14+ years of experience helping product teams fix performance, accessibility, and frontend architecture at scale."
keywords: "front-end developer, frontend specialist, web performance, accessibility, frontend architecture"
page_css: home
open_graph:
  image: "imgs/layout/preview-image.webp"
---

<header class="hero" id="top">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero__inner">
            <div class="hero__left">
                <h1>Hi, I'm Amanda Vilela :)</h1>
                <p class="hero__lead">
                    <mark
                        >I help product teams fix performance,
                        accessibility, and frontend architecture at
                        scale.</mark
                    >
                </p>
                <p>
                    Frontend specialist with 14+ years of experience
                    working with startups, agencies, and large-scale
                    platforms. I partner with teams to identify systemic
                    issues, align technical decisions, and deliver
                    measurable improvements in performance,
                    accessibility, and maintainability.
                </p>
                <nav
                    class="hero__actions"
                    aria-label="Quick navigation"
                >
                    <a href="mailto:hello@amandavilela.me" class="btn"
                        >Contact me →</a
                    >

                    <a href="/services" class="btn"
                        >Consulting services →</a
                    >
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="hero__right" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="hero__profile">
                    <img
                        class="hero__profile-img"
                        src="/imgs/layout/profile.webp"
                        alt="Profile picture"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<main id="main-content">
    <section class="focus" id="focus" aria-labelledby="focus-heading">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title" id="focus-heading">
                What I focus on
            </h2>
            <ul class="focus__grid" role="list">
                <li class="focus__card">
                    <h3 class="focus__card-title">
                        Performance &amp; Core Web Vitals
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Improve real user metrics and eliminate
                        bottlenecks affecting conversion and experience
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="focus__card">
                    <h3 class="focus__card-title">Accessibility</h3>
                    <p>
                        Ensure products are usable, compliant, and
                        scalable across teams
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="focus__card">
                    <h3 class="focus__card-title">
                        Frontend architecture
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Help teams make better technical decisions,
                        reduce complexity, and build systems that scale.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="focus__card">
                    <h3 class="focus__card-title">
                        Technical Leadership
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Aligning developers, reduce friction, and create
                        an effective engineering environment.
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" />

    <section
        class="how-i-work"
        id="how-i-work"
        aria-labelledby="how-heading"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title" id="how-heading">How I work</h2>
            <p class="how-i-work__lead">
                I work closely with product and engineering teams,
                combining deep technical analysis with practical
                execution.
            </p>
            <ul class="bullet-list" role="list">
                <li class="bullet-list__item">
                    Diagnose root causes (not just symptoms)
                </li>
                <li class="bullet-list__item">
                    Prioritize based on business impact
                </li>
                <li class="bullet-list__item">
                    Align teams on sustainable solutions
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" />

    <section
        class="engagement"
        id="services"
        aria-labelledby="engagement-heading"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title" id="engagement-heading">
                Engagement formats
            </h2>
            <p class="engagement__subtitle">How we can work together</p>
            <ul class="engagement__grid">
                <li class="engagement__cell">
                    <h3>Audit</h3>
                    <p class="engagement__desc">
                        Clear diagnosis + prioritized action plan.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="engagement__cell">
                    <h3>Project-based</h3>
                    <p class="engagement__desc">
                        Direct involvement in specific initiatives.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="engagement__cell">
                    <h3>Workshops</h3>
                    <p class="engagement__desc">
                        Hands-on training tailored to your team.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="engagement__cell">
                    <h3>Retainer</h3>
                    <p class="engagement__desc">
                        Ongoing support with async + Slack access.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="engagement__cell">
                    <h3>1:1 or group sessions</h3>
                    <p class="engagement__desc">
                        A focused session you can use however you need.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="engagement__cell engagement__cell--link">
                    <a
                        class="engagement__cta"
                        href="/services/"
                    >
                        Learn more →
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section
        class="contact"
        id="contact"
        aria-labelledby="contact-heading"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title" id="contact-heading">
                Let's work together
            </h2>
            <p>
                If you're looking to improve your product's performance,
                accessibility, or frontend quality, I can help.
            </p>
            <p>
                Reach me at
                <a
                    href="mailto:hello@amandavilela.me"
                    class="contact__email"
                    >hello@amandavilela.me</a
                >
                for a quick chat or a detailed quote.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="latest-post" aria-labelledby="latest-post-heading">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title" id="latest-post-heading">Blog</h2>
            {% set featuredPost = collections.featured[0] %}
            {% set latestPost = collections.posts[0] %}
            {% set post = featuredPost if featuredPost else latestPost %}
            
            {% if post %}
            <article class="latest-post__card post-summary">
                <h3 class="post-summary__title">
                    <a class="post-summary__link" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </h3>
                <time class="post-summary__date" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">
                    {{ post.date | readableDate }}
                </time>
                {% if post.data.description %}
                <p class="post-summary__description">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
            </article>
            <a href="/blog/" class="latest-post__view-all">View all posts →</a>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
